## Key things 
- Users are only allowed to answer once
- Correct answer are highligthed white and coloured green i.e the text
- user are allowed to switch to any question he/she wants.
## Features
- Interactive quiz interface with multiple-choice questions that helps to develop users mathematically.
- Countdown timer for added challenge which helps the user to grow/develop faster.
- Winning and losing images based on performance i.e the result of the user.
- Dynamic results display.
- Scientific Calculator button which aids the user.
- Prize for every question.
